nodes.text: Journey to Mos Eisley is a children's book by Golden Books that explores the events on Tatooine during Star Wars: Episode IV A New Hope.

Join Luke Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi as they embark on a mission to a wretched hive of villains—the Mos Eisley spaceport! This classic space adventure is illustrated with actual photos from the Special Edition STAR WARS TRILOGY!
